lead_paragraph: Japan's Hideki Matsuyama made light work of tough conditions at the WGC-HSBC Champions with a sparkling seven-under-par 65 to surge ahead of a stellar field after the second round at a wet and windy Sheshan International Golf Club on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Matsuyama Turns on Style to Take Lead in Windy Shanghai
